title: Global AI Race: India Emerges As World’s 3rd Most Competitive AI Power
description: India has emerged as the world’s third most competitive country in artificial intelligence, according to Stanford University’s Global AI Vibrancy Tool on Sunday. The latest ranking highlights how India’s fast-growing tech ecosystem and strong talent base are helping the country play a key role in the global AI race.
